%% seq_08_project_management.mmd
%% Updated 2026-06-16.
%% Scope: Project management overview across user and organization surfaces.
%% Detail files:
%%   - seq_08a_project_create_member_add.mmd
%%   - seq_08b_project_delete.mmd
%% Note:
%%   - TransferProjectOwnershipCommand exists but no route is wired, so it is omitted here.

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Org Member
    participant B as Browser
    participant UI as Inertia Project UI
    participant C as Controller
    participant API as Project API
    participant Cmd as Command
    participant Repo as Repository
    participant Evt as Event Bus

    Note over U, Evt: LIST SURFACE SPLIT
    U->>B: Open project workspace
    B->>C: GET /projects or GET /org/projects
    C-->>UI: Render user table or org ProjectGrid
    UI-->>B: /projects uses AppLayout, /org/projects uses OrganizationLayout

    Note over U, Evt: CREATE OR GROW PROJECT
    U->>UI: Submit org project form or add member
    UI->>C: POST /org/projects or POST /projects/members
    C->>Cmd: CreateCurrentOrganizationProjectCommand or AddProjectMemberCommand
    Cmd->>Repo: Persist project or member record
    Cmd->>Evt: Emit project:created or project:member_added
    C-->>B: Redirect back

    Note over U, Evt: SHARED DETAIL EDIT
    U->>UI: Edit shared project detail
    UI->>API: PUT /api/projects/:id
    API->>Cmd: UpdateProjectCommand
    Cmd->>Repo: Validate status and persist update
    API-->>UI: JSON success or validation error

    Note over U, Evt: DELETE PROJECT
    U->>B: Delete project
    B->>API: DELETE /api/projects/:id or DELETE /projects/:id
    API->>C: Route to API or page controller
    C->>Cmd: DeleteProjectCommand
    Cmd->>Repo: Validate blockers and soft delete project
    Cmd->>Evt: Emit project:deleted
    C-->>B: Redirect to projects list
